00:19:18,470 --> 00:19:20,220
Hand it over!

241
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:25,140
Why would Older Brother want this broken pearl anyway?

242
00:19:38,060 --> 00:19:41,070
I can't! The pearl is stuck and it can't be taken out.

243
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:44,370
If you want it, you should also take my hand.

244
00:19:44,370 --> 00:19:46,370
Xin Fa.

245
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:50,090
Right, right, right! Xin Fa, Xin Fa...

246
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:18,230
Brother don't have any questions after reading it, do you?

247
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:21,770
Then I'll read it again.

248
00:20:21,770 --> 00:20:25,710
Why did I have to say that? I'm done for this time.

249
00:20:26,870 --> 00:20:28,370
Forget it!

250
00:20:28,930 --> 00:20:31,420
Xiao Chun Hua wouldn't trick me.

251
00:20:32,890 --> 00:20:34,830
Naturally, of course.

252
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:37,710
Right, Older Brother.

253
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:41,870
I already gave you the Xin Fa. In the future,

254
00:20:41,870 --> 00:20:44,510
can you not come to see me anymore?

255
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:55,410
Do you really hate me this much?

256
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:02,670
As soon as you got engaged, you wanted to get rid of me.

257
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,900
How would I dare?

258
00:21:08,850 --> 00:21:11,510
Xiao Chun Hua still doesn't understand.

259
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:14,480
Trying to find true love with your demon-like appearance,

260
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:17,090
is just a delusional thinking.

261
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:20,390
In the end, you'll just be used by Xiao Bai.

262
00:21:20,390 --> 00:21:22,940
Xiao Bai wouldn't do that.

263
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:29,180
I also want to be as beautiful as Older Brother.

264
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:31,430
Even if a woman is innately beautiful,

265
00:21:31,430 --> 00:21:33,270
it still doesn't guarantee her true love.

266
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:36,320
I've seen it happen before.

267
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:40,640
You have seen it happen before!

268
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,630
Do I know them?

269
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:47,570
A woman loved someone who used her.

270
00:21:47,570 --> 00:21:50,330
She endured all those needless, bitter struggles...

271
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:52,830
How foolish!

272
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:56,530
Do Xiao Chun Hua also want to become someone like that?

273
00:21:56,530 --> 00:21:58,360
Who is that woman?

274
00:21:58,360 --> 00:22:00,730
Who is her lover?

275
00:22:05,210 --> 00:22:07,510
You don't need to know these things.

276
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:11,140
You need only to remember that

277
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:13,910
in this world, only your older  brother loves you sincerely.

278
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:19,040
Older Brother, it's already late, so it's best if you go back and rest early.

279
00:22:19,040 --> 00:22:23,640
If anyone sees me giving you the Xin Fa, I'll certainly be dead.

280
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:28,240
If you are so scared of death, then why don't you wear the silk ice pearl?

281
00:22:29,210 --> 00:22:30,590
Okay.

282
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:43,400
Fortunately, I have two hands.

283
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,790
This is my lotus lantern.

284
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:39,200
My wish is to be together with Older Brother Xiao for eternity.

285
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:41,140
Never will we part.

286
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:01,620
Sect Master Xiao.

287
00:24:09,710 --> 00:24:13,030
Sect Master Xiao is also here to enjoy the night.

288
00:24:20,170 --> 00:24:25,820
Before arriving here, I already heard tales describing what beautiful scenery the lotus flowers make.

289
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:29,980
However, it's quite regrettable that the flowers have already started to wither.

290
00:24:33,970 --> 00:24:36,470
Sect Master Xiao, the weather is becoming cold.

291
00:24:36,470 --> 00:24:38,990
You even dumped the medicine out—

292
00:24:41,570 --> 00:24:45,220
The lotus flowers withered and the lotus seeds began to grow.

293
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:47,740
Are the lotus seeds bitter,

294
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:50,430
or is this medicine bitter?

295
00:24:51,980 --> 00:24:56,000
Miss Chun Hua, what do you think?

296
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:59,220
They are both bitter.

297
00:25:00,410 --> 00:25:04,080
It's just that I didn't think Sect Master Xiao would be afraid of bitterness.

298
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:05,830
Afraid?

299
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:23,730
Miss Chun Hua,

300
00:25:23,730 --> 00:25:27,560
you have to keep this secret for this old man.

301
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:48,140
Why does he come here in the middle of the night to dump medicine in the lotus pond?

302
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,400
So strange!

303
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:17,600
Father, I didn't disappoint your expectation.

304
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:22,030
I finally mastered Xiao Xiao Fengming Saber's last technique.

305
00:26:29,930 --> 00:26:31,740
Xiao Bai.

306
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:39,310
You should go and see Sect Master Xiao.

307
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:52,110
Mastering Xiao Xiao Fengming Saber's last move

308
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:54,940
was also from a fortunate encounter.

309
00:26:56,640 --> 00:27:01,470
Twenty years ago, thanks to my friend,

310
00:27:01,470 --> 00:27:06,180
I received this ice stone lotus which smoothed my pathway.

311
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:10,860
Thereafter, I was able to master Fengming Saber's last move.

312
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:14,880
Today, I want to pass it onto you.

313
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:18,470
Xiao'er, keep it carefully!

314
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:50,180
Now you obtained the stone lotus, you can soon master Fengming Saber’s

315
00:27:50,180 --> 00:27:52,270
 last technique. 

316
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:55,490
You must remember, once you learn it fully,

317
00:27:55,490 --> 00:27:59,340
then you, the saber, and the stone lotus will become one.

318
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:03,020
None of them can be separated.

319
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:06,550
You must remember well. Remember it!

320
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,740
Could it be that father...

321
00:28:22,610 --> 00:28:24,950
Miss Chun Hua, I will see my father first.

322
00:28:24,950 --> 00:28:27,260
You should go back to rest for now.

323
00:28:27,870 --> 00:28:31,830
Xiao Bai, I'm always here.

324
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:39,850
Have you ever regretted it?

325
00:28:39,850 --> 00:28:42,280
If it would happen again,

326
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:46,090
