It's your mother, right?

352
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:14,490
The person is already dead so what is the point in holding on?

353
00:31:14,490 --> 00:31:17,420
The most important person is Xiao Chun Hua.

354
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:20,150
I do not want this Xin Fa anymore.

355
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:24,310
