359
00:31:34,470 --> 00:31:37,300
The timing right now is perfect.

360
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:48,830
Shangguan Qiu Yue, what does that mean?

361
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:52,560
The timing that you met me,

362
00:31:52,560 --> 00:31:57,760
